  "text": "Use will be made from the German Socio-Economic Panel (GSOEP). 11 The data are the same as used by [CITATION_1] except that I only concentrate on the 1999-wave. 12 As I will show, the essential result of zero correlation in the Winkelmann-set up will be retained.",
